OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fsunny into the evening, with clear
OL,7,Fspells overnight, cloud increasing
OL,8,Ffrom the west towards dawn. Much
OL,9,Fcooler than recent nights. Mostly
OL,10,Flight southwesterly winds, but always
OL,11,Fa little breezier near coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA bright or sunny start,
OL,14,Fparticularly across the east of the
OL,15,Fregion. Skies turning hazy, leading to
OL,16,Fbright spells during the afternoon.
OL,17,FTemperatures close to the late June
OL,18,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
