OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FLargely dry with sunny spells next
OL,7,Fweek, but a few showers possible at
OL,8,Ftimes, particularly on Tuesday. Light
OL,9,Fwinds. Feeling pleasant in the
OL,10,Fsunshine with near normal temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
